    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index within 12% of experimental measurements across the assessed operating envelope. It is noted that edge cases near stall and cavitation inception were not fully covered by the validation dataset and represent a known limitation of the current evidence base. The assessment team concludes that the model is sufficiently credible for the intended COU and the decision outcome is Accepted.",
